{
  "stem": "26142.8",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Had we gone in there, we would have stayed-- stayed-- it's an uncle!",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It's my mother's younger brother.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But one daughter, she was 16 years of age, one managed to escape from there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And she is the only survivor.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They got all murdered in-- in Stanislau.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So that hand that we saw, that was stretched out, was to know to get in.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The city was empty.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Where wouldn't we go in?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I mean, the locals were showing up.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So-- I'm not finished.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The locals left this one house, because there-- there was a dentist in that family.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And in this little village, they-- he was the only dentist.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And one of the Ukrainian [NON-ENGLISH] knew what the-- what they are doing there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So he told them to stay inside, and we are not going to torture your family.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because they needed-- they needed a dentist.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that dentist, after we stayed there for Yom Kippur, we didn't know what happened in Yom Kippur.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But after Yom Kippur, he went out, the dentist went out to work.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He told us later what happened in that place where they-- where they massacred-- they-- they rounded all of them up and massacred them in Stanislau.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We always talk about the-- this girl lives in Ra'anana now.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "She has a nice family built up.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And-- and-- and-- I always-- when I'm in Israel-- I stay with her, because she is to me like a-- like a sister.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So that miracle-- we-- we got through there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that dentist-- we asked him if he can find us also a man with a buggy.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we always told the guy that we have a paper from the German command, you know.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That had some-- it-- it-- it helped us one-- one time.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
